{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"Range.surroundContents","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Range/surroundContents","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Range\"><code>Range</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Constructor</summary><ol><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Range/Range\"><code>Range()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>属性</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Range/collapsed\"><code>collapsed</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Range/commonAncestorContainer\"><code>commonAncestorContainer</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Range/endContainer\"><code>endContainer</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Range/endOffset\"><code>endOffset</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Range/startContainer\"><code>startContainer</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Range/startOffset\"><code>startOffset</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>方法</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Range/cloneContents\"><code>cloneContents()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Range/cloneRange\"><code>cloneRange()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Range/collapse\"><code>collapse()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Range/compareBoundaryPoints\"><code>compareBoundaryPoints()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Range/compareNode\"><code>compareNode()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Range/comparePoint\"><code>comparePoint()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Range/createContextualFragment\"><code>createContextualFragment()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Range/deleteContents\"><code>deleteContents()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Range/detach\"><code>detach()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Range/extractContents\"><code>extractContents()</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Range/getBoundingClientRect\"><code>getBoundingClientRect()</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Range/getClientRects\"><code>getClientRects()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Range/insertNode\"><code>insertNode()</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Range/intersectsNode\"><code>intersectsNode()</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Range/isPointInRange\"><code>isPointInRange()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Range/selectNode\"><code>selectNode()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Range/selectNodeContents\"><code>selectNodeContents()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Range/setEnd\"><code>setEnd()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Range/setEndAfter\"><code>setEndAfter()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Range/setEndBefore\"><code>setEndBefore()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Range/setStart\"><code>setStart()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Range/setStartAfter\"><code>setStartAfter()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Range/setStartBefore\"><code>setStartBefore()</code></a></li><li><em><code>surroundContents()</code></em></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Range/toString\"><code>toString()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>继承</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/AbstractRange\"><code>AbstractRange</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n<p><strong><code>Range.surroundContents()</code>&nbsp;</strong>方法将 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Range\"><code>Range</code></a> 对象的内容移动到一个新的节点，并将新节点放到这个范围的起始处。</p>\n\n<p>这个方法与&nbsp;<code>newNode.appendChild(<a href=\"/en-US/DOM/range.extractContents\" title=\"en/DOM/range.extractContents\">range.extractContents()</a>); <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/range/insertNode\" title=\"/en-US/docs/DOM/range.insertNode\">range.insertNode</a>(newNode)</code> 等价。应用以后，&nbsp;<code>newNode</code>&nbsp;包含在 <code>range</code>&nbsp;的边界点中。</p>\n\n<p>然而，如果 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Range\"><code>Range</code></a> 断开了一个非 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Text\"><code>Text</code></a> 节点，只包含了节点的其中一个边界点，就会抛出异常。也就是说，不像上述的等价方法，如果节点仅有一部分被选中，则不会被克隆，整个操作会失败。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"语法","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\"><em>range</em>.surroundContents(<em>newParent</em>);\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"参数","title":"参数","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"newparent\"><code>newParent</code></dt>\n <dd>一个包含内容的 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Node\"><code>Node</code></a>。</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"example","title":"示例","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"html","title":"HTML","isH3":true,"content":"<pre class=\"notranslate\">&lt;span class=\"header-text\"&gt;Put this in a headline&lt;/span&gt;</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"javascript","title":"JavaScript","isH3":true,"content":"<pre class=\"notranslate\">const range = document.createRange();\nconst newParent = document.createElement('h1');\n\nrange.selectNode(document.querySelector('.header-text'));\nrange.surroundContents(newParent);</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"结果","title":"结果","isH3":true,"content":"<p><iframe class=\"sample-code-frame\" title=\"Example sample\" id=\"frame_example\" src=\"https://yari-demos.prod.mdn.mozit.cloud/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Range/surroundContents/_sample_.example.html\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe></p>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"规范","id":"specification","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://dom.spec.whatwg.org/#dom-range-surroundcontents","title":"DOM Standard"}],"query":"api.Range.surroundContents"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性","isH3":false,"query":"api.Range.surroundContents","dataURL":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Range/surroundContents/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"参见","title":"参见","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document_Object_Model\" title=\"/en-US/docs/DOM/DOM_Reference\">The DOM interfaces index</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"语法","id":"syntax"},{"text":"示例","id":"example"},{"text":"规范","id":"specification"},{"text":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性"},{"text":"参见","id":"参见"}],"summary":"Range.surroundContents() 方法将 Range 对象的内容移动到一个新的节点，并将新节点放到这个范围的起始处。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Range.surroundContents()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Range.surroundContents()","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Range.surroundContents()","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/api/range/surroundcontents","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/api/range/surroundcontents/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发技术"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API 接口参考"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Range","title":"Range"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Range/surroundContents","title":"Range.surroundContents"}],"pageTitle":"Range.surroundContents - Web API 接口参考 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}